name: bucket o' fluffin'
description:
You get the fluffin' for $22!! Bucket is not included, for display purposes only.

6 full ounces all fluffed up the fluffin fills a 15" round by 9" tall bucket. :) 

Fluffin' comes sealed in a poly bag.  Open the bag, remove the fluffin and just fluff it up like crazy. The longer it's out of the bag, the fluffier it gets.  I suggest getting a quart sized zip seal bag to keep your fluffin' in between sessions.  

Fluffin' is a great basket/bucket filler, you can roll it and use it to help position baby instead of using big lumpy socks. It is also great for needle felting!!
